abstract: Police say Phoenix man detained for questioning in series of shootings around Interstate 10 is not prime suspect; police are still seeking information on 11 reported shootings, none fatal, which have unsettled area motorists, some of whom remember similar episode from decade ago.
lead_paragraph: The man is considered a person of interest in the case, and officials are pursuing other leads in the shootings, which began on Aug. 29 and have been unnerving drivers.

headline.main: Police Rule Out Detained Man, 19, as Prime Suspect in Phoenix Freeway Shootings
